Hello, thank you for calling West Barnstable Horse Hides, your favorite local bowling alley. My name is Alex. May I ask who I have the pleasure of speaking with today?

Hi Alex, my name is Jamie.

Hi Jamie, nice to meet you. How can I assist you with our services today?

I'm calling about a billing issue I noticed on my last visit.

I'm sorry to hear that, Jamie. Let me help you sort this out. Could you please provide me with the date of your visit?

Sure, it was on October fifth.

Thank you for that information. Could you also provide your booking reference number? It should be on your receipt or confirmation email.

Yes, the booking reference number is A one two three B four five six.

Great, thank you, Jamie. I will look into this right away and resolve the issue. We appreciate your patience.

Thank you, Alex. I appreciate your help.

You're welcome, Jamie. Thank you for reaching out to us. Is there anything else I can assist you with today?

No, that's all. Thanks again.

Alright, have a great day, Jamie. Thank you for calling West Barnstable Horse Hides. Goodbye!
